    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi dei aeterni. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/32">Karolus</persName> divina clementia
                            <rs key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Cunctis sancte dei aeclesiae
                        nostrisque fidelibus presentibus videlicet et futuris cognitum fieri
                        volumus, eo quod <persName key="#Intercessory #fidelisOf"><name
                                ref="Liutwardus">Liutuardus</name></persName> noster <rs
                            key="#fidelisOf">fidelis</rs> adiit nostram <rs key="#Intercessory"
                            >clementiam</rs> et humiliter nostrae pietatis suggessit de quodam <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abbate</rs>
                        <persName key="#Abbots"><name ref="Iohannepertus"
                            >Iohanneperto</name></persName> nomine, qui praeesse videtur in <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> quod dcitur <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/148" key="#Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            >Tolla</orgName> asserens, quod <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs>
                        <persName key="#Abbots"><name ref="Deusdedit">Deusdedit</name></persName>,
                        qui ante illum praefuerat in ipso monasterio, emerit res quasdam in
                        proprietatem illi coenobio; postea vero neglegentia quadam aliquantae
                        firmitates de illa emptione disperditae sunt. Ob hoc supplicavit nostram
                        clementiam, ut tam ipsas res, quas praefatus abbas Deusdedit per <rs
                            key="#Cartula">cartulas</rs> sive <rs key="#Privileges">monimina</rs>
                        vel quocumque ingenio adquisivit quamque et alias res, quae deo auspice in
                        reliquum adquirere potuerint, sub nostri <rs
                            key="#Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium">muntburdi defensionem et perpetuae
                            augustalis praecepti tuitionem</rs> suscipere signaremur. Nos autem pro
                        nostrae mercedis intuitu humili supplicationi adsensum prebentes decrevimus
                        per hoc nostrae auctoritatis preceptum, ut nullus ex comitibus
                        gastaldionibus iudicibus seu nostris ministerialibus pro predictis rebus
                        positis in <placeName ref="#places/1846"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            >Cadinario</placeName>, <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            >Legrolo</placeName>, <placeName ref="#places/1844"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            >Adilio</placeName> sive <placeName ref="#places/1845"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            >Casa nova</placeName> ac <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Tuitio/bannum/mundeburdium"
                            >Uidriano</placeName> vel aliis locis et rebus ipsius monasterii
                        ubicumque adiacentibus sive positis sive pro his, que iuste adquirere
                        potuerint, contra illos querelare audeat, sed liceat eos <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >quieto et pacifico ordine frui</rs>. Si quis autem contra hoc nostrae
                        auctoritatis precepto regia auctoritate edito illos molestare praesumpserit,
                            <rs key="#Penalty">decem libras auri obrizi</rs> componere cogatur, <rs
                            key="#Camera_regis">medietatem camerae nostrae</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem illis
                            fratribus</rs>, quibus molestiam inferre presumpserit. Haec vero nostrae
                        confirmationis praecepto ut per futura tempora ratam ac stabilem optineat
                        firmitatem, manu propria subter ea confirmavimus et anuli nostri impressione
                        adsiggillari iussimus. Signum (MF) domni Karoli serenissimi regis.
                                <persName><name ref="Deusdedit">Deusdedit</name></persName> advicem
                        domni <persName key="#Archchancellor" ref="#people/33">Liutuardi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Archchancellor">archicancellarii</rs> recognovi (SI D). Data XII
                        kal. Ian. Anno ab incarnatione domini DCCCLXXX, indictione XIIII, anno domni
                        Karoli piissimi regis in Francia V, in Italia II; actum civitate <placeName
                            ref="#places/43">Placentia</placeName>; in dei nomine feliciter
                        amen.</ab>
